<i>Megachile circumcincta</i> <font size="-1" face="sans-serif">&#40;Kirby, 1802&#41;</font></b><br>
<small><i>Apis circumcincta </i>Kirby, 1802; <i>Megachile giliae </i>Cockerell, 1906; <i>Megachile circumcincta var lactescens </i>Cockerell, 1928; <i>Megachile circumcincta var griseohirta </i>Alfken, 1929; <i>Megachile circumcincta var insidiosa </i>Benoist, 1940; <i>Megachile &#40;Macromegachile&#41; circumcincta ozbeki </i>Tkalc&#367;, 1977; <i>Megachile &#40;Delomegachile&#41; circumcincta numidica </i>Tkalc&#367;, 1988; <i>Megachile &#40;Macromegachile&#41; circumcincta etnaensis</i> van der Zanden, 1989; Megachile &#40;Xanthosaurus&#41;_sic circumcincta chinensis_homonym Wu, 2006; <i>Megachile circumcincta lactescens </i>Cockerell, 1928; <i>Megachile &#40;Delomegachile&#41; giliae </i>Cockerell, 1906; <i>Megachile &#40;Xanthosarus&#41; giliae </i>Cockerell, 1906</small><p>
